Miyauchi A, Onishi T, Morimoto S, Takai S, Matsuzuka F, Kuma K, Maeda M, 
Kumahara Y.

Plasma calcitonin (CT) levels were measured serially in 54 patients surgically 
treated for medullary thyroid carcinoma. Patients with postoperative basal CT 
levels higher than 1 ng/ml measured within 1 month after surgery had a higher 
recurrence rate than those with lower CT levels (p less than 0.002). Patients 
